languages.text:
{n}Ulfar's voice becomes low and heavy with dire warning:{/n}
"Stand aside, young brother,
Our foe is wounded,
but well-banked is his malice
and still smouldering;
My lot will be
his blow to meet;
My hide ere carries
scars aplenty."

